=> Interpolation:
-> Interpolation is the insertion fo something of a different nature into something else.
//

=> String Interpolation or String formatting:
-> The process of inserting on oboject into a predefined is called string interpolation or string formatting.


======================================================================================================================================================================


=> %-formatting:

name="Rafi"
print("My name is %s." %name)

A="Islam"
print("His Name is %s."%A)

number=55
print("The Integer number is %d" %number)

num=70285
print("The float number is %f" %num)

num=5.02
print("The Double number is %d" %num)

name='Rafiul'
city='Bangladesh'
print("My name is %s and I live in %s ðŸ˜‚." %(city,name))

name="Rakib"
address="Gaibandha sadar Gaibandha"
print("I am %s And My address %s." %(name,address))



